ygData.subject: Re: Looking for a few good men (and women)
ygData.msgSnippet: if you have a magic weapon just go kill wisps in the w commons on the east side near the skel tower, i got 3 g stones in a row took me 2 minutes to get 12
ygData.messageBody:
if you have a magic weapon just go kill wisps in the w commons on the east side near the skel tower, i got 3 g stones in a row

took me 2 minutes to get 12 plat, the wisps all spawn in the same spot and star out if you spot the spawn you can make a killing
